{
  "texts": [
    "R2R contains 90 indoor scenes with 7189 trajectories.",
    "REVERIE replaces the fine-grained instructions in R2R with high-level instructions to locate remote objects.",
    "R4R concatenates two adjacent tail-to-head trajectories in R2R, forming longer instructions and trajectories.",
    "RxR contains much more complex instructions and trajectories than R2R.Since CLIP [18] is pretrained on English language data, we use the English subset of RxR (both en-IN and en-US) for verification, which includes 26464, 2939, 4551 pathinstruction pairs for Training, Val Seen, and Val Unseen, respectively.",
    "Evaluation Metrics."
  ]
}